Depth Charge/Cheetor/Tigerhawk/Rhinox/Silverbolt/CF




Depth Charge did a U-turn in mid air to dodge the shots. He fired two 
missles from hs rocket laucher at Demon Wulf.






~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


Cheetor looked down at Iris. " you will not be able to defeat me. 
every move you make I learn from that. face it you are out classed." 
He pulled back his whip waiting for Iris to get up.



~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Tigerhawk flew infront of Rhinox taking the shots for him.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Rhinox went on the side of Tigerhawk and he fired 25 rouns out of 
each gun at Unitron.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Silverbolt fired two missles at Demon Wulf.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The Cf shields were down to 30% and falling with every shot.
